char mon[12][4]={"JAN", "FEB", "MAR", "APR", "MAY", "JUN", "JUL", "AUG", "SEP", "OCT", "NOV", "DEC"};

int days[12]={31,28,31,30,31,30,31,31,30,31,30,31};
int fin_mon(char *str)
{
	for(int i=0;i<12;i++) if(str[0]==mon[i][0]&&str[1]==mon[i][1]&&str[2]==mon[i][2]) return i;
}
int main()
{

    int t;
    int d,m,y;

    char str[15];
    scanf("%d",&t);
    for(int l=1;l<=t;l++)
    {
    	scanf("%s",str);
    	d=0;
    	d+=str[0]-'0';
    	d=d*10+str[1]-'0';
    	m=fin_mon(str+3);
    	y=0;
    	for(int i=7;i<11;i++) y=10*y+str[i]-'0';
    	sum=0;
    	for(int i=0;i<m;i++)sum+=days[i];
    	sum+=d;
    	if(y%400==0&&m>1) sum++;
    	else if(y%4==0&&y%100!=0&&m>1) sum++;
    	if(sum<=300) printf("Case %d: %d Hundreds\n",l,sum);
    	else if(sum<=360) printf("Case %d: %d Tens\n",l,sum-300);
    	else printf("Case %d: %d Ones\n",l,sum-360);
    }

}
